{
  "texts": [
    "As depicted in example (ii) in Fig 4, the BERN2 tagged entity may not contain the entity name at all.",
    "Such entity relations are incomplete, and thus should be eliminated.",
    "For larger datasets, the use of BERN2 to process each word in an entity name can become computationally expensive.",
    "To address this issue, we created a list of the most repetitive non-entity words (available on the Gene-Interaction-Extraction GitHub repository Fig 4.",
    "Gene name refinement using BERN2."
  ]
}